description: DSTX adheres to a systematic process, including only those stocks that meet the firm’s proprietary cash-flow-based valuation and quality criteria. Our security selection focuses on U.S. stocks with low debt levels and stable cash flows. We then invest in the most attractively valued remaining 100 companies based on Distillate Capital’s normalized free cash flow methodology.
name: Distillate International Fundamental Stability & Value ETF
